      "comment": "JACKTAVERN TAZ (4) got around 400m in a solid 24.35 when winning an A8 at this track last start. In form and looks the one to beat again. SENTOSA SUNSET (2) was game in defeat off a low draw at the latest outing, finishing second and beaten a neck (24.81) behind Ballyard Alfie at this track. Will give a great sight again. SEOMRA OYSTER (6) was out of the money two runs back then improved sharply last time to score at this track over 400m (24.44). Goes up a notch but will give backers a sight. SMASHING MAJOR (1) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
